["name"] = [=[Teea Danger Alerts]=],
["versionNote"] = [=[Hey guys! I'm back, so I'm updating my WAs once again, including my Danger Alerts.
This is a partial update, which includes several specs, minor changes to visuals and some changes to the core. I will update it with more specs later.

As some of you may know, I never asked or accepted any donations before. But now, if you like my work and wish to donate, I'd gladly accept a TWW key (gift won't work), so I can play on my main account.  
[Here's more information about it in my Discord if you wonder why](https://discord.com/channels/935226620044783668/936321641238110238/1298788939519496253)

Changes:
- Reverted some of the changes made by Gismo to visual aspect of WA to the original look
- Changed visual texts for class and specialization to make it shorter
- Made several changes to the core (the stuff under the hood)
- Now all updated specs will display PI as lowest priority (this doesn't include specs which weren't updated yet)
- Now all updated specs will take in count PI and the main stat proc/use trinket when calculating Danger Level in combination with other auras
- Updated Arcane Mage
- Updated Fire Mage
- Updated Frost Mage
- Updated Affliction Warlock
- Updated Demonology Warlock
- Updated Destruction Warlock
- Updated Balance Druid
- Updated Shadow Priest
- Updated Windwalker Monk
- Updated Feral Druid]=],
