["versionNote"] = [=[Hey guys! I'm back, so I'm updating my WAs once again.

As some of you may know, I never asked or accepted any donations before. But now, if you like my work and wish to donate, I'd gladly accept a TWW key (gift won't work), so I can play on my main account.  
[Here's more information about it in my Discord if you are interested](https://discord.com/channels/935226620044783668/936321641238110238/1298788939519496253)

Changes:
- Added Surging Totem
- Changed some default settings]=],
